quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  25,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  25,1,nihayat mutbarrik hai woh jis ne yeh Farqan apne bande par nazil kya taakay saaray Jahan walon ke liye Nazeer ho
  25,2,"woh jo zameen aur asmano ki badshahi ka maalik hai, jis ne kisi ko beta nahi banaya hai, jis ke sath badshahi mein koi shareek nahi hai, jis ne har cheez ko peda kya phir is ki aik taqdeer muqarrar ki"
  25,3,"logon ne ussay chore kar aisay mabood bana liye jo kisi cheez ko peda nahi karte balkay khud peda kiye jatay hain, jo khud apne liye bhi kisi naffa ya nuqsaan ka ikhtiyar nahi rakhtay, jo nah maar satke hain nah jِla satke hain, nah marey hue ko phir utha satke hain"
  25,4,jin logon ne NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki baat maan-ne se inkaar kar diya hai woh kehte hain ke yeh Farqan aik mann gharat cheez hai jisay iss shakhs ne aap hi ghurr liya hai aur kuch dosray logon ne iss kaam mein is ki madad ki hai bara zulm aur sakht jhoot hai jis par yeh log utar aeye hain
  25,5,kehte hain yeh puranay logon ki likhi hui cheeze hain jinhein yeh shakhs naqal karta hai aur woh isay subah o shaam sunai jati hain
  25,6,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho ke"" isay nazil kya hai uss ne jo zameen aur asmano ka bhaid jaanta hai"" haqeeqat yeh hai ke woh bara ghafoor Raheem hai"
  25,7,"kehte hain"" yeh kaisa rasool hai jo khana khata hai aur baazaaron mein chalta phirta hai? kyun nah is ke paas koi farishta bheja gaya jo is ke sath rehta aur ( nah maan-ne walon ko ) dhmkata ?"
  25,8,"ya aur kuch nahi to iss ke liye koi khazana hi utaar diya jata, ya is ke paas koi baagh hi hota jis se yeh ( itminan ki ) rozi haasil karta"" aur zalim kehte hain"" tum log to aik sehar zada aadmi ke peechay lag gay ho """
  25,9,"dekho, kaisi kaisi ajeeb hujjtein yeh log tumahray agay paish kar rahay hain, aisay behke hain ke koi thikaane ki baat inn ko nahi sojhti"
  25,10,"bara babarkat hai woh jo agar chahay to un ki tajweez kardah cheezon se bhi ziyada barh charh kar tum ko day sakta hai, ( aik nahi ) bohat se baagh jin ke neechay nehrein behti hon, aur barray barray mehal"
  25,11,"asal baat yeh hai ke yeh log"" uss gharri"" ko jhutla chuke hain aur jo uss gharri kojhutla-ay is ke liye hum ne bharakti hui aag muhayya kar rakhi hai"
  25,12,woh jab daur se inn ko dekhe gi to yeh uss ke ghazab aur josh ki aawazian sun len ge
  25,13,aur jab yeh dast o pa basta uss mein aik tang jagah thonse jayen ge to apni mout ko pukarnay lagen ge
  25,14,( uss waqt un se kaha jaye ga ke ) aaj aik mout ko nahi bohat si mouton ko poukaro
  25,15,"inn se pucho, yeh injaam acha hai ya woh Abdi jannat jis ka wada khuda tars parhaiz garon se kya gaya hai? jo unn ke aamaal ki jaza aur unn ke safar ki aakhri manzil ho gi"
  25,16,"jis mein unn ki har khwahish poori ho gi, jis mein woh hamesha hamesha rahen ge, jis ka ataa karna tumahray parvar-digaar ke zimmay aik wajib alada wada hai"
  25,17,"aur woh wohi din ho ga jab ke ( tumhara rab ) inn logon ko bhi ghair laaye ga aur un ke unn mabodon ko bhi bُla le ga jinhein aaj yeh Allah ko chore kar پوج rahay hain, phir woh unn se pouchye ga"" kya tum ne mere inn bundon kar gumraah kya tha? ya yeh khud raah e raast se bhatak gay thay? """
  25,18,"woh arz karen ge"" pak hai aap ki zaat, hamari to yeh bhi majaal nah thi ke aap ke siwa kisi ko apna maula banayen magar aap ne inn ko aur un ke baap dada ko khoob samanِ zindagi diya hatta ke yeh sabaq bhool gay aur shamat zada ho kar rahay """
  25,19,"yun jhutla den ge woh ( tumahray mabood ) tumhari unn baton ko jo aaj tum keh rahay ho, phir tum nah apni shamat taall sakuu ge nah kahin se madad pa sakuu ge aur jo bhi tum mein se zulm kere usay hum sakht azaab ka maza chkhayin ge"
  25,20,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum se pehlay jo rasool bhi hum ne beje hain woh sab bhi khana khanay walay aur baazaaron mein chalne phirnay walay log hi thay darasal hum ne tum logon ko aik dosray ke liye azmaish ka zareya bana diya hai kya tum sabr karte ho? tumhara rab sab kuch daikhta hai"
  25,21,"jo log hamaray huzoor paish honay ka andesha nahi rakhtay woh kehte hain"" kyun nah farishtay hamaray paas beje jayen? ya phir hum apne rab ko dekhen"" bara ghamand le baithy yeh apne nafs mein aur hadd se guzar gay yeh apni sar kashi mein"
  25,22,"jis roz yeh firshton ko dekhen ge woh mujrimon ke liye kisi basharat ka din nah hoga, cheekh utheen ge ke panah ba khuda"
  25,23,aur jo kuch bhi un ka kya dhara hai ussay le kar hum gubhar ki terhan ura den ge
  25,24,bas wohi log jo jannat ke mustahiq hain uss din achi jagah tehrayge aur dopehr guzarnay ko umdah maqam payen ge
  25,25,aasman ko cheerta howa aik baadal is roz namodaar ho ga aur firshton ke paray ke paray utaar diye jayen ge
  25,26,uss roz haqeeqi badshahi sirf Rehman ki ho gi aur woh munkareen ke liye bara sakht din ho ga
  25,27,"zalim ensaan apna haath chuba-ay ga aur kahe ga"" kash mein ne rasool ka sath diya hota"
  25,28,"haae meri kam bakhti, kash mein ne falan shakhs ko dost nah banaya hota"
  25,29,"uss ke b_hkaye mein aa kar mein ne woh nasiyaat nah maani jo mere paas aayi thi, shetan ensaan ke haq mein bara hi be wafa nikla """
  25,30,"aur rasool kahe ga ke"" ae mere rab, meri qoum ke logon ne is quran ko nishana tazheek bana liya tha """
  25,31,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne to isi terhan mujrimon ko har nabi ka dushman banaya hai aur tumahray liye tumhara rab hi rahnumai aur madad ko kaafi hai"
  25,32,"munkareen kehte hain"" iss shakhs par sara quran aik hi waqt mein kyun nah utaar diya gaya ?"" haan, aisa is liye kya gaya hai ke is ko achi terhan hum tumahray zehan nasheen karte rahen aur ( isi gharz ke liye ) hum ne is ko aik khaas tarteeb ke sath allag allag ajzaa ki shakal di hai"
  25,33,"aur ( is mein yeh Maslehat bhi hai ) ke jab kabhi woh tumahray samnay koi nirali baat ( ya ajeeb sawal ) le kar aeye, uss ka theek jawab Bar waqt hum ne tumhe day diya aur behtareen tareeqay se baat khol di"
  25,34,jo log avndhe mun jahannum ki taraf dhkile jaane walay hain un ka muaqqaf bohat bura aur un ki raah hadd darja ghalat hai
  25,35,hum ne moose ko kitaab di aur is ke sath is ke bhai haroon ko madadgaar ke tor par lagaya
  25,36,aur unn se kaha ke jao uss qoum ki taraf jis ne hamari ayaat ko jhutla diya hai aakhir-kaar unn logon ko hum ne tabah kar ke rakh diya
  25,37,yahi haal qoum Nooh ka howa jab unhon ne Rasolo-n ki tkzib ki hum ne unn ko ghark kar diya aur duniya bhar ke logon ke liye aik nishaan Ibrat bana diya aur un zaalmon ke liye aik dard naak azaab hum ne muhayya kar rakha hai
  25,38,isi terhan Aad aur smod aur ashaab ulrasaur beech ki sadiiyon ke bohat se log tabah kiye gay
  25,39,aur un mein se har aik ko hum ne ( pehlay tabah honay walon ki ) misalein day day kar samjhaya aur aakhir kaar har aik ko ghaarat kar diya
  25,40,aur uss bastii par to inn ka guzar ho chuka hai jis par bad tareen barish brsayi gayi thi kya unhon ne is ka haal dekha nah ho ga? magar yeh mout ke baad doosri zindagi ki tawaqqa hi nahi rakhtay
  25,41,"yeh log jab tumhe dekhte hain to tumhara mazaq bana letay hain ( kehte hain )"" kya yeh shakhs hai jisay khuda ne rasool bana kar bheja hai ?"
  25,42,"iss ne to hamein gumraah kar ke apne mabodon se bur-ghashta hi kar diya hota agar hum unn ki aqeedat par jim nah gay hotay"" acha, woh waqt daur nahi hai jab azaab dekh kar aِnhin khud maloom ho jaye ga ke kon gumraahi mein daur nikal gaya tha"
  25,43,kabhi tum ne uss shakhs ke haal par ghhor kya hai jis ne apni khwahish nafs ko apna khuda bana liya ho? kya tum aisay shakhs ko raah e raast par laane ka zimma le satke ho ?
  25,44,"kya tum samajte ho ke un mein se aksar log suntay aur samajte hain? yeh to janwaron ki terhan hain, balkay unn se bhi gay guzray"
  25,45,tum ne dekha nahi ke tumhara rab kis terhan saya phela deta hai? agar woh chahta to usay daimi saya bana deta hum ne Sooraj ko uss par Daleel banaya
  25,46,phir ( jaisay jaisay Sooraj uthta jata hai ) hum is saaye ko rafta rafta apni taraf samettay chalay jatay hain
  25,47,"aur woh Allah hi hai jis ne raat ko tumahray liye libaas, aur neend ko sakoon-e mout, aur din ko jee uthnay ka waqt banaya"
  25,48,aur wohi hai jo apni rehmat ke agay agay hawaon ko basharat bana kar bhejta hai phir aasman se pak pani nazil karta hai
  25,49,taakay aik murda ilaqay ko is ke zariye zindagi bakhshay aur apni makhlooq mein se bohat se janwaron aur insanon ko sairaab kere
  25,50,"is karishmay ko hum baar baar un ke samnay laatay hain taakay woh kuch sabaq len, magar aksar log kufar aur nashukri ke siwa koi dosra rawayya ikhtiyar karne se inkaar kar dete hain"
  25,51,agar hum chahtay to aik aik bastii mein aik aik Nazeer utha khara karte
  25,52,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kafiroon ki baat hargiz nah manu aur is quran ko le kar un ke sath jehaad kabeer karo"
  25,53,"aur wohi hai jis ne do samndron ko mila rakha hai aik lazeez o sheree, dosra talkh o shore aur dono ke darmain aik parda haail hai aik rukawat hai jo inhen good mid honay se rokay hue hai"
  25,54,"aur wohi hai jis ne pani se aik bashar peda kya, phir is se nasb aur sasural ke do allag silsilay chalaye tera rab bara hi qudrat wala hai"
  25,55,"is khuda ko chore kar log unn ko پوج rahay hain jo nah un ko naffa pouncha satke hain nah nuqsaan, aur oopar se mazeed yeh ke kafir apne rab ke muqablay mein har baaghi ka madad gaar bana howa hai"
  25,56,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum ko to hum ne bas aik Mubasher aur Nazeer bana kar bheja hai"
  25,57,"inn se keh do ke"" mein is kaam par tum se koi aُjrt nahi mangta, meri aُjrt bas yahi hai ke jis ka jee chahay woh apne rab ka rasta ikhtiyar kar le """
  25,58,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, uss khuda par bharosa rakho jo zindah hai aur kabhi marnay wala nahi is ki hamd ke sath is ki tasbeeh karo apne bundon ke gunaaho se bas usi ka bakhabar hona kaafi hai"
  25,59,"woh jis ne chay dinon mein zameen aur aasman ko aur unn saari cheezon ko bana kar rakh diya jo aasman o zameen ke darmain hain, phir aap hi ( kaayenaat ke takhat saltanat )"" arsh"" par jalva farma howa rehman, is ki shaan bas kisi jan-nay walay se pucho"
  25,60,"inn logon se jab kaha jata hai ke is Rehman ko sajda karo to kehte hain"" Rehman kya hota hai? kya bas jisay to keh day isi ko hum sajda karte phiren ?"" yeh dawat un ki nafrat mein ulta aur izafah kar deti hai"
  25,61,bara mutbarrik hai woh jis ne aasman mein burj banaye aur is mein aik chairag aur aik chamakta chaand roshan kya
  25,62,"wohi hai jis ne raat aur din ko aik dosray ka janasheen banaya, har is shakhs ke liye jo sabaq lena chahay, ya shukar guzaar hona chahay"
  25,63,Rehman ke ( asli ) bande woh hain jo zameen par naram chaal chaltay hain aur jaahil un ke mun ko ayen to keh dete hain ke tum ko salam
  25,64,jo apne rab ke huzoor sjday aur qiyam mein raatain guzartay hain
  25,65,"jo duayen karte hain ke"" ae hamaray rab, jahannum ke azaab se hum ko bacha le, uss ka azaab to jaan ka laago hai"
  25,66,"woh bara hi bura mstqr aur maqam hai """
  25,67,"jo kharch karte hain to nah fuzool kharchi karte hain nah bukhal, balkay un ka kharch dono ant_haon ke darmain aitdaal par qaim rehta hai"
  25,68,"jo Allah ke siwa kisi aur mabood ko nahi pukarte, Allah ki haraam ki hui kisi jaan ko na-haq halaak nahi karte, aur nah zina ke murtakib hotay hain yeh kaam jo koi kere woh apne gunah ka badla paye ga"
  25,69,qayamat ke roz is ko mkrrr azaab diya jaye ga aur isi mein woh hamesha zillat ke sath para rahay ga
  25,70,ila yeh ke koi ( un gunaaho ke baad ) tauba kar chuka ho aur imaan laa kar amal Saleh karne laga ho aisay logon ki buraiyon ko Allah bhulaiyon se badal day ga aur woh bara ghafoor Raheem hai
  25,71,jo shakhs tauba kar ke naik amli ikhtiyar karta hai woh to Allah ki taraf palat aata hai jaissa ke palatnay ka haq hai
  25,72,( aur rehman ke bande woh hain ) jo jhoot ke gawah nahi bantay aur kisi laghu cheez par un ka guzar ho jaye to shareef admion ki terhan guzar jatay hain
  25,73,jinhein agar unn ke rab ki ayaat suna kar nasiyaat ki jati hai to woh is par andhay aur behray ban kar nahi reh jatay
  25,74,"jo duayen manga karte hain ke"" ae hamaray rab, hamein apni biwion aur apni aulaad se aankhon ki thandak day aur hum ko parhaiz gaaron ka imam bana """
  25,75,yeh hain woh log jo apne sabr ka phal manzil buland ki shakal mein payen ge aadaab o tasleemaat se unn ka istaqbaal ho ga
  25,76,woh hamesha hamesha wahan rahen ge kya hi acha hai woh mstqr aur woh maqam
  25,77,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, logon se kaho"" mere rab ko tumhari kya haajat pari hai agar tum is ko nah poukaro ab ke tum ne jhutla diya hai, anqareeb woh saza pao ge ke jaan chhrhani mahaal ho gi """
